{
  "stem": "3206.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever I did, it was OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever I-- as long as I didn't bother him too much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was in that farm, you know, my mother was by herself, and she had to support me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was working very hard, very hard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not on the farm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was-- beside what she was working on the farm, she was like a peddler.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was going all over the-- between the farmers she was gathering, like, bottles and selling something, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From that, she made a living to support me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was with her till seven years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, somehow, afterwards, when I came back to Staszow from that farm, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somehow they got together back, my father and mother.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whether through me or not, they got together back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was the only thing that's supporting what was from my brothers and sisters, which they were working.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was the support, what we got, all of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Otherwise, there was nothing was major to come in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was together with us, sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were all together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was the only one to cook for everybody, you know, to clean, to cook.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole family was living in one room-- one room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was two beds, and it was there we were working in that same room at daytime.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At nighttime, we pushed away on the side, and we took out some boards with chairs put together, and we were sleeping in it. with a-- our mattress was straw stuffed in a bag.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was the mattress.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was very nice, lovingly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, this was not like families here-- jealousy, with things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
